videos.headline: UConn freshmen connect for game's 1st TD
videos.description: UConn scores the first touchdown of the game as freshman QB Jack Zergiotis finds freshman WR Matt Drayton in the end zone for the score.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (UConn freshmen connect for game's 1st TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Porter speeds into end zone for Houston TD
videos.description: Houston RB Kyle Porter weaves through the defense and scores from 12 yards out to give the Cougars a 10-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Porter speeds into end zone for Houston TD) 2019/10/19
